Voters in Slovakia choose representatives for all 150 National Council seats. While anti-migrant Prime Minister Robert Fico's Smer party is expected to lose its parliamentary majority, it should be in position to lead a coalition government. (Reuters via Firstpost) (New Europe), (Bloomberg)Charlot Salwai is elected Prime Minister of Vanuatu following the January snap election. Salwai takes office the same day. (ABC News)